{"tid":1162250,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"謗佛的人要落地獄","createTime":"2019-05-19T18:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T06:15:47.000Z","uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2059517f0b5a114109885245b4606760296d6883","tid":1162250,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:01:26.000Z","msg":"《地藏十輪經》：「或於我說與聲聞乘相應正法，誹謗輕毀，障蔽隱沒，不令流布；或於我說與獨覺乘相應正法，誹謗輕毀，障蔽隱沒，不令流布；或於我說與無上乘相應正法，誹謗輕毀，障蔽隱沒，不令流布；或於歸我諸出家人，若是法器、若非法器，多行忿恨，呵罵毀辱，譏刺輕诮，種種誹謗，隱善揚惡，廣說乃至起輕慢心種種觸惱，如是諸人非聖法器。」<br />\n<br />\n挑佛經毛病嘅人係會：「從此命終，墮三惡趣，受無量種增上猛利難忍苦毒，經於無量百千俱胝那庾多劫，難復人身。」<br />\n<br />\n姐係從此輪迴不得做人！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家以為噏少句，積下陰德！！"},{"pid":"622fa5444ca09c3030654224de14eea4bf7891d6","tid":1162250,"uid":231523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:03:41.000Z","msg":"嗯嗯"},{"pid":"a833639dcc9340251aa0dc0a2912ed8a9e976ee7","tid":1162250,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"622fa5444ca09c3030654224de14eea4bf7891d6","tid":1162250,"uid":231523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:03:41.000Z","msg":"嗯嗯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:04:21.000Z","msg":"誠心忠告！"},{"pid":"1588fd536c8fe79027b2417adef8130414d9ec25","tid":1162250,"uid":231523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:06:14.000Z","msg":"你知唔知佛教，都有唔同傳承㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09e7f24fdbee284dedc1f481495e9cb0e59f501","tid":1162250,"uid":51039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1588fd536c8fe79027b2417adef8130414d9ec25","tid":1162250,"uid":231523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:06:14.000Z","msg":"你知唔知佛教，都有唔同傳承㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:09:18.000Z","msg":"所以你想講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7311d14941c950ad08676da0793440499cd0d5","tid":1162250,"uid":231523,"like